The paper proposes a deep learning-based generative model for ETA estimation that relies on historical data of a particular bus route. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
